com.nokia.maps.kml

Interface LineStyle

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ColorStyle

    public interface LineStyle
extends ColorStyle
    This interface represents the <LineStyle> tag from KML specification. Specifies the drawing style (color, color mode, and line width) for all line geometry.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String ELEMENT
      This constant defines <LineStyle> as an XML element for styling for a line.
      static java.lang.String WIDTH
      This constant defines the width of a line.
